T1  - A framework for the analysis of financial reforms and the cost of official safety nets
AU  - Isard, Peter
AU  - Mathieson, Donald J.
AU  - Rojas-Suárez, Liliana
JO  - Journal of Development Economics
VL  - 50
IS  - 1
SP  - 25
EP  - 79
